  "description": {
    "zh": "Gemini CLI 中文速查表，整理交互模式、REPL 命令、MCP、扩展、配置文件与常用环境变量。",
    "en": "Gemini CLI cheat sheet covering interactive flows, REPL commands, MCP, extensions, configuration files, and common environment variables."
  },
  "versionInfo": {
    "zh": "Google Gemini CLI",
    "en": "Google Gemini CLI"
  },
