    "href": "https://geminicli.com/docs/",
    "label": {
      "zh": "📋 资料来源",
      "en": "📋 Sources"
    },
    "items": [
      {
        "zh": "基于 Gemini CLI 官方文档、CLI cheatsheet、settings 与 configuration 页面整理",
        "en": "Compiled from the official Gemini CLI docs, CLI cheatsheet, settings, and configuration pages"
      },
      {
        "zh": "覆盖交互启动、REPL 命令、MCP、扩展、认证与项目级配置",
        "en": "Covers interactive startup, REPL commands, MCP, extensions, authentication, and project-level configuration"
      },
      {
        "zh": "重点保留终端里最常查的命令、路径和配置项",
        "en": "Focuses on the commands, paths, and config knobs you most often need in the terminal"
      },
      {
        "zh": "适合快速扫读、A4 横向打印与团队内贴墙",
        "en": "Designed for quick scanning, A4 landscape printing, and pinning in a team workspace"
      }
    ]
  },
  "columns": [
